file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://apirest-192-168-1-58-swag.on.stack.lol'
    description: Local
info:
  description: ''
  version: 0.1.0
  title: SWAG REST API
  termsOfService: ''
  contact:
    email: ''
tags:
  - name: auth
    description: Authentication
  - name: payment
    description: Payment
paths:
  /payment/create-charge:
    post:
      tags:
        - payment
      summary: Create a payment charge
      description: >-
        [Stripe docs](https://stripe.com/docs/connect/destination-charges#create-a-charge)
      responses:
        '405':
          description: Invalid input
      parameters:
        - name: amount
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
          example: 10000
        - name: fee
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
          example: 5000
        - name: currency
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
          example: eur
        - name: destination
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          example: pk_test_51HalJJHQaAykIZ0jxGhjBjUZMh7ShjlKiCKA0gM9CtQrV12bW8N4eXIcnwqNQxf9sB8q8oleUZP9gitVQKuk20Ny00BzbLYi9c
    summary: ''
    description: ''
components:
  schemas:
    ApiResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        type:
          type: string
        message:
          type: string
  links: {}
  callbacks: {}
security: []
